creator: Pedro Antonio de Alarcón y Ariza; François Coppée; Alphonse Daudet; Gustavo Adolfo Bécquer;  Benito Pérez Galdós; André Theuriet; Armando Palacio Valdés; Marcel Prévost; Antoinette Ogden; Antoine Gustave Droz; Jules Simon; Maxime Du Camp
description:
LibriVox recording of Christmas Stories from French and Spanish Writers by Pedro Antonio de Alarcón y Ariza; François Coppée; Alphonse Daudet; Gustavo Adolfo Bécquer; Benito Pérez Galdós; André Theuriet; Armando Palacio Valdés; Marcel Prévost; Antoinette Ogden; Antoine Gustave Droz; Jules Simon; Maxime Du Camp.
Read in English by David Wales
Fifteen short stories from French and Spanish writers of many times. - Summary by david wales
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
